<s> I only have one thing to add to this excellent response.  </s>
<s> It does not matter where you put the reset button, as long as you provide a safety valve for it.  </s>
<s> If the reset button is activated, you can ask whether or not the user wants to continue with reset or not.  </s>
<s> I do agree though that reset should be provided in a place that is not in the way of the submit button.  </s>
<s> The problem with putting it after the submit button though is that some people might want to use it but not find it.  </s>
